<plot>Junghoon arrives in town with his son perpetually strapped to his chest to get back his estranged wife. Instead of the warm greeting he expected, Yoomi is shocked to see Junghoon and Jimmy. When it is revealed that Yoomi's mother, Mrs. Song, engineered their reunion in hopes of convincing Junghoon to leave Jimmy with her to raise, Junghoon must make a choice between an unfettered life, free from all ties, or assume the responsibility of fatherhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?235154</url></doc>
